<lb ed="C I" n="0213a00"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><head type="no">No. 78</head>
<lb ed="C I" n="0213a00"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>比丘道政四十人等造像記</title></jhead></juan>
<lb ed="C I" n="0213a01"/><p id="pI01p0213a0101">維大齊河清三年歲次甲申四月己丑朔十三日庚子敬造。若夫至理玄寂。非言無以詮其景
<lb ed="C I" n="0213a02"/>行。道宗沖<note n="0213001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31020;＝邃【史】</note><app n="0213001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邃</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31020;</rdg></app>。匪功何以表其盛德。至迺擾擾四生。皆出入於存亡之境。<note n="0213002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00502;＝驅【史】</note><app n="0213002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">驅</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00502;</rdg></app><app source="0213002" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">驅</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00502;</rdg></app>萬<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">有</unclear>。僉去來於是
<lb ed="C I" n="0213a03"/>非之路。幻術雖形。駛電已滅。輪迴不息。循環豈已。非建弘<note n="0213003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31021;＝業【史】</note><app n="0213003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">業</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31021;</rdg></app>。意奉靈<note n="0213004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31022;＝津【史】</note><app n="0213004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">津</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31022;</rdg></app>。昏<note n="0213005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31023;＝惑【史】</note><app n="0213005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">惑</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31023;</rdg></app>之鄣誰減。明達之
<lb ed="C I" n="0213a04"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">旨</unclear>焉致。然有北豫州州都白水王府行參軍兼別駕毛叉。擢本八桂之藂。抽芳鄧林之菀。播才
<lb ed="C I" n="0213a05"/>俊於<note n="0213006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31024;＝望【史】</note><app n="0213006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">望</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31024;</rdg></app>府。藉地厚於嚮家。識　　　　惠清<note n="0213007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31029;＝遠【史】</note><app n="0213007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遠</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31029;</rdg></app>。人為水鏡。器量<note n="0213008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31025;＝遐【史】</note><app n="0213008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遐</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31025;</rdg></app>濟。才實通理。苦空無我。便損
<lb ed="C I" n="0213a06"/>七尺之軀。緣<note n="0213009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31026;＝假【史】</note><app n="0213009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">假</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31026;</rdg></app>非有。不　　　　　<note n="0213010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31027;＝吝【史】</note><app n="0213010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">吝</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31027;</rdg></app>千金之貨。仍有比丘僧道政。德行淹潤。負素<note n="0213011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31028;＝攸【史】</note><app n="0213011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">攸</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31028;</rdg></app><note n="0213012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB21284;＝顯【史】</note><app n="0213012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">顯</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB21284;</rdg></app>。洗心
<lb ed="C I" n="0213a07"/>法水。構情道際。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">共</unclear>相經紀。　出入存　功。遂　　率邑義卌人等。選自福田。瞻言勝地。在垣&CB31045;
<lb ed="C I" n="0213a08"/>寺<note n="0213013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31029;＝所【史】</note><app n="0213013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31029;</rdg></app>。敬造石像一區。石　　採嵩華。匠追揚鄴。麗絕圖繢。妙盡真容。北佩鄭邑。是桓武之<note n="0213014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30486;＝舊【史】</note><app n="0213014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">舊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30486;</rdg></app>事。
<lb ed="C I" n="0213a09"/>南面形□。瞰由產之　盛<app source="0213003" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">業</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31021;</rdg></app>。左帶二水。乃延智者之居。右瞻三山。仍屬仁者之宅。千藂百&CB00031;。異
<lb ed="C I" n="0213a10"/>　色同　榮。葉　蔽陰連。少知星月。流遁之容。<note n="0213015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">淂＝得【史】</note><app n="0213015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">得</lem><rdg wit="【原】">淂</rdg></app>道入門。負笈之夫。陟遊忘返。宗門俊德。器令
<lb ed="C I" n="0213a11"/>是飾。荷　　錫名僧。豈<app source="0213007" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遠</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31029;</rdg></app>千里。<note n="0213016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31030;＝戒【史】</note><app n="0213016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">戒</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31030;</rdg></app>行清苦。必存十善之識。言念至　　誠。詎違六時之道。馴馴
<lb ed="C I" n="0213a12"/>恂恂。邕邕穆穆。真有鹿菀之風。不無<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">象</unclear>山之誨。敬羨嘉處。建茲功　　德。其詞曰。
<lb ed="C I" n="0213a13"/>無小無大。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">薨</unclear>想伊歸。誰窮誰達。溘盡為非。&CB01302;人明識。惠此<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">津</unclear>機。濟時以道。<note n="0213017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30591;＝拯【史】</note><app n="0213017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">拯</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30591;</rdg></app>手垂衣。
<lb ed="C I" n="0213a14"/>苦海揚波。火宅炎盛。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">多</unclear>淦汲引。昇此究竟。逐迷<app source="0213015" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">得</lem><rdg wit="【原】">淂</rdg></app>杆。<app source="0213009" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">假</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31026;</rdg></app>我明命。膺感不休。功興已<note n="0213018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB15137;＝竟【史】</note><app n="0213018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">竟</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB15137;</rdg></app>。
<lb ed="C I" n="0213a15"/>　道生四諦。空起三門。白鵝致善。烏鴨<note n="0213019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31031;＝與【史】</note><app n="0213019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">與</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31031;</rdg></app>恩。<note n="0213020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30695;＝靈【史】</note><app n="0213020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">靈</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30695;</rdg></app>&CB00528;弘烈。敢庶斯存。鐫石功紀。固本深
<lb ed="C I" n="0213a16"/>相。理尚沖寂。道真清　　素。絕塵自此。和光匪處。崔嵬高山。浮丘已過。潺湲流水。濯
<lb ed="C I" n="0213a17"/>嬰是趨。</p>
